text: Fresnay-sur-Sarthe is a commune. It is found in the region Pays de la Loire in the Sarthe department in the west of France. On 1 January 2019, the former communes of Coulombiers and Saint-Germain-sur-Sarthe were merged into Fresnay- sur-Sarthe.Arrêté préfectoral 30 November 2018 == References == Category:Communes in Sarthe
title: Fresnay-sur-Sarthe
